To install rvm run following command
 https://rvm.io/rvm/install
 i use
gpg --keyserver hkp://keys.gnupg.net --recv-keys 409B6B1796C275462A1703113804BB82D39DC0E3
\curl -sSL https://get.rvm.io | bash -s stable --ruby

After this two ommands 
right click on terminal -> profile -> profile preferences -> select command from tab bar -> click check run command as login shell
Restart terminal
type command
  rvm list
